{"tid":283462,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【倫敦沖天火】恐有塌樓危機　消防：多人身亡","createTime":"2017-06-14T07:42:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-16T00:14:35.000Z","uid":20933,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"10b8eb98793bcbf3f872d45f4c47b46ff1d3511b","tid":283462,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T07:42:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170614/s00005/7744da90bfd4ab8003e9720949065bef.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170614%2Fs00005%2F7744da90bfd4ab8003e9720949065bef.jpg&h=f8e8dfcf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n倫敦西部一幢樓高至少24層的大廈，當地時間凌晨發生大火，整幢大樓被燒通頂，至少50人送院治理，有目擊者指有人跳樓逃生。消防證實事故中多人身亡，但未掌握死亡人數。倫敦市長簡世德指，是次意外是「重大事故」，當局出動逾200名消防員、40輛消防車灌救。<br />\n<br />\n事發於當地周三凌晨1時許，現場是倫敦西部的Grenfell Tower，大火焚燒至今仍未撲熄。整幢大樓幾乎被大火吞噬，濃煙升上半空，窗框被燒至變形。當局指，至少50人送院治理，消防證實有人喪生，但未掌握死亡人數。<br />\n<br />\n據《每日郵報》報道，現場消息指大樓有塌樓危機，警方正疏散附近市民。<br />\n<br />\n居於大樓4樓的生還者Zoe指，火警發生時濃煙密佈，但她指大樓火警鐘沒響起。另外，第一時間到達現場的目擊者馬丁指，有人從大樓跳樓逃生，亦有母親抱着嬰兒在窗戶旁等候救援，現場尖叫聲不斷。馬丁欲幫忙救人，但找不到大樓的逃生出口。<br />\n<br />\n及時逃出大樓的生還者暫時被安置在附近的社區中心。有生還者稱，不知火警發生，直至鄰居大叫才回過神來，「我算是非常幸運，有很多人來不及逃走」，他相信家中所有物品已被燒毀。有生還者指，撤離大樓時情况非常混亂，有人敲打鄰居的門提醒其他人要撤離。<br />\n<br />\n據報，涉事大樓興建於1974年，有120個住宅單位，相信有200人居住。當地消防指，大樓二樓首先起火，火勢其後蔓延至頂層，形容是大型、非常嚴重的意外。"},{"pid":"2ab6d1f99fb74ae181efb2916c90e3cedb356074","tid":283462,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T07:42:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170614/s00005/1497425703501\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170614%2Fs00005%2F1497425703501&d=sTNgRDBrZD5brF%2FPtSnklTA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=5838a811\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170614%2Fs00005%2F1497425703501&h=7d61b2d1\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170614/s00005/1497425703501</a>"},{"pid":"25dfe9bb9edadcad80c66ec1b52169a14579c1e0","tid":283462,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T07:50:39.000Z","msg":"2 樓起火 死硬啦<br />\n恐襲？"},{"pid":"64bd43cc3a1ad80f524908283e45b3cc873b1637","tid":283462,"uid":42820,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T07:52:10.000Z","msg":"皇天擊殺"},{"pid":"1662a0dba3d21a6391d2fa2619f79c2e4767dade","tid":283462,"uid":46644,"like":2,"dislike":9,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T07:58:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"af2fabc6b80df0c6990b4d3dbae7f0b7e7faa78f","tid":283462,"uid":55575,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T07:59:47.000Z","msg":"住呢度全部移民啡皮豬黎<br />\n去揾阿拉拎72處女啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f28f3d0122b9a0a76239d1f68794d2fbcdbe1229","tid":283462,"uid":55597,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T08:00:17.000Z","msg":"中國沖天火，一燒就好似紙紮咁，一陣就收皮"},{"pid":"7da365d69e47260ccb8129fc29ba61df3dd9744f","tid":283462,"uid":4493,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T08:00:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/14/160024_57874106260e09bcfca1cc823d01f081.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F14%2F160024_57874106260e09bcfca1cc823d01f081.jpg&h=7d88c308&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n6/70年代英國有唔少丨"},{"pid":"77b2c39dcd5b1c0f5637dd3d4a38d44abadc6ccf","tid":283462,"uid":4493,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T08:01:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/14/160024_57874106260e09bcfca1cc823d01f081.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F14%2F160024_57874106260e09bcfca1cc823d01f081.jpg&h=7d88c308&s={SIZE}\" /><